{"tid":869880,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"無謂談自己","createTime":"2018-10-20T15:23:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T15:25:13.000Z","uid":68255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"284fb15c6779bcf5a58e9a133087a27eb97f4c8e","tid":869880,"uid":68255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T15:23:56.000Z","msg":"只有自卑　屬於我<br />\n做不起討好角色　期望誰發現愛惜　<br />\n六十歲也只得我自己　得到甚麼　<br />\n相信戀愛　不信可以被愛<br />\n差了甚麼　習慣了孤單去過　不必伸手救我<br />\n<br />\n好中<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   21歲人 未拍過拖 覺得自己好差 做咩都做唔好 好憎自己 無女仔無鍾意自己<br />\n六十歲也只得我自己 習慣了孤單去過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ba2182becdf9079a28f73dfb5cd7699e9566d5","tid":869880,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T15:24:31.000Z","msg":"毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd5bc18714e5a248fa9b9bf8d42dd33b1b242e76","tid":869880,"uid":68255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7ba2182becdf9079a28f73dfb5cd7699e9566d5","tid":869880,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T15:24:31.000Z","msg":"毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T15:25:13.000Z","msg":"毒撚真係好on9"}]}